data.title: Appeal Court Paris Judgement
data.meta_description: Appeal court Paris Judgement  - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document is a request from a French lawyer to the High Court of Paris for a copy of a judgment from July 6, 2017 by the 32nd Correctional Courtroom (Case No. 11203092048). The lawyer's client, a banking institution, wants to understand the reasoning behind the court's decision, which found the bank responsible for money laundering and sentenced it. The lawyer is asking for a copy of the trial documents to allow the client to conduct a jurisprudential study.
